WAKEFIELD RATTAN CO. v. TAPPAN. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. December 6, 1893.) Action by the Wakefield Rattan Company against Shepherd Tappan.

Argued before MAYHAM, P. J., and PUTNAM and HERRICK, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for reargument granted. See 24 N. Y. Supp. 430.
